#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/templates/halfdragon_template.md:2
msgid "# Half-Dragon Template"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/templates/halfdragon_template.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"A beast, humanoid, giant, or monstrosity can become a half-dragon. It keeps "
"its statistics, except as follows.    \n"
"**Challenge**. To avoid recalculating the creature's challenge rating, apply "
"the template only to a creature that meets the optional prerequisite in the "
"Breath Weapon table below. Otherwise, recalculate the rating after you apply "
"the template.    \n"
"**Senses**. The half-dragon gains blindsight with a radius of 10 feet and "
"darkvision with a radius of 60 feet.    \n"
"**Resistances.** The half-dragon gains resistance to a type of damage based "
"on its color. \n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/templates/halfdragon_template.md:15
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| Color               | Damage Resistance |\n"
"|---------------------|-------------------|\n"
"| Black or copper     | Acid              |\n"
"| Blue or bronze      | Lightning         |\n"
"| Brass, gold, or red | Fire              |\n"
"| Green               | Poison            |\n"
"| Silver or white     | Cold              |\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/templates/halfdragon_template.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Languages**. The half-dragon speaks Draconic in addition to any other "
"languages it knows.    \n"
"**New Action: Breath Weapon.** The half-dragon has the breath weapon of its "
"dragon half. The half-dragon's size determines how this action functions.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/templates/halfdragon_template.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"| Size             | Breath Weapon      | Optional Prerequisite |\n"
"|------------------|--------------------|-----------------------|\n"
"| Large or smaller | As a wyrmling      | Challenge 2 or higher |\n"
"| Huge             | As a young dragon  | Challenge 7 or higher |\n"
"| Gargantuan       | As an adult dragon | Challenge 8 or higher |\n"
msgstr ""
